### install useing

- npm install tailwindcss @tailwindcss/cli

### create two file inside of asset folder

- input.css [ here include import tailwindcss]
- output.css [ here inclue all style code]

### when this website style tailwindcss then use blow command for show

- npx @tailwindcss/cli -i ./assets/input.css -o ./assets/output.css --watch

### At last template.liquid file include blow command must be in header

# - {{ 'output.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }} or {{'style.css | asset_url | stylesheet_tag}}

### Note: components name not be cmaleCase for example homePage.liquid that is worng.then current is hoempage.liquid
